ing against , so the democrats need to tie everyone to trump & amp ; his atrocious policies not just his hideous personality . what we know is that * all * proven cases of election fraud were by republicans . whether trump ’ s followers are very stupid or very corrupt is something only they know . trump supporters need to acknowledge the larger republican party is ready to take back control of the party . you can attack each of these participants but they know the man much better than those he has pandered to for their support . such a situation would make it possible to really get rid of trump . if the gop is successful in the 2022 midterms , then trump will still be in a great position to try to get revenge in 2024 . it 's all about political strategy here . we must vote blue in november 2022 . for the gop , therefore , the room for maneuver is narrow at the moment . by alienating trump , the republicans would risk losing a lot of popular support . they must therefore leave trump at the center of the political game & amp ; hope for a defeat at the midterms in 2022 . the republicans have wanted to get rid of trump since the end of his presidential term , but they are unable to do so for strategic reasons . trump lost , but he got record support for a presidential loser . this means that trump is still extremely popular . trump committed all the crimes you wanted hillary clinton ’ s head for , & amp ; yet you ’ re condoning what trump has done . the republican silence on this matter is deafening . they have no defense for any of this & amp ; they know damn well it ’ s even worse than what they accused clinton of . but now we know that trump & amp ; his administration did exactly the same things they accused hillary of . there 's no “ lock him up ! ” from republicans . in fact , nothing is coming from republicans at all . releasing the seditionists from responsibility will be the next step toward the disassembling of democracy . trump ca n't give up running for president . it 's a tremendous cash generator for him & amp ; it shields him from his legal problems . we must vote blue in november 2022 . if the republicans take over congress in 2022 , the first act will be to shut down the january 6th commission . that means trump , bannon , meadows & amp ; the rest of the seditionists will be off the hook .
