 war on syria ? but if obama started it , it had to be justified because democrats uphold law & amp ; democracy . https : //t.co/jdobol3qnn are the democrats creating a situation in which biden is forced to issue a pardon to trump in order to expedite getting his appointees in place and moving his legislative agenda forward ? what is interesting & amp ; quite dangerous is that everything the state is doing with its attempt to criminalize & amp ; repress everyone who voted or supported trump was predicted by radical right . they are using these moves to actually consolidate a proto-fascist movement in the u.s. is it arrogance or just some kind of strange cognitive disorder that causes liberals to wonder why millions of voters raise questions about biden 's legitimacy . liberals who build a movement on trump 's `` illegitimacy . '' https : //t.co/gwilmngvko do n't forget when obama administration resupplied israel in the middle of their slaughter of innocents in gaza in 2014 . obama , biden , trump , the democrats & amp ; racist corporate media are all complicit with the war crimes and crimes against humanity that israel is committing . `` lucky : how joe biden barely won the presidency , '' a book on last year 's primary that confirmed my arguments that democrats were more concerned with defeating sanders than trump & amp ; that if sanders had won the top funders of party would have supported trump ! biden & amp ; democrats are more dangerous than trump because like trump they are also committed to maintain global white power but are just more refined . in the popular imagination white supremacists act like trump while the `` atlanticists '' ( white supremacists ) like biden get a pass i want to raise another question to my morally superior & amp ; intelligent liberal & amp ; radical friends who supported biden & amp ; democrats . is there a difference between netanyahu 's brand of right-wing , racist fascism & amp ; trump ? and is that why biden supports netanyahu ?