rstood & amp ; was more honest than racist democrats that issue of china could be racialized . the biden negotiated pact between u.k. & amp ; white supremacist settler states of the u.s. & amp ; australia against china is a natural one with its meaning quite clear , if not openly stated . the so-called crisis being played out in the democrat party is a fraud . the progressives who already gave away too much will agree to significantly reduced & amp ; delayed spending on items they say are vital . the real issue for democrats is retaining the `` trump '' tax cuts . by gutting the bbb of its most popular elements , democrats have no language on plight of working class & amp ; have ensured that they will lose one , & amp ; probably both the senate & amp ; house in 2022 . like their radical hanger-ons , the obsession with trump has distorted their vision . support democracy in nicaragua by condemning the election interference of the rogue u.s. state . there is absolutely no difference between the right-wing trump forces & amp ; right-wing neoliberal democrats on issue of u.s. imperialism , except the `` left '' tends to side with democrats . look at the cynical racial politics being played by democrats & amp ; black misleaders on voting rights . the democrats were supposed to come back in january & amp ; pass build back better , instead the new priority is voting rights . in other words , class politics are trumped for identity . supreme court struck down pre-clearence provision of vra in 2013 under your first black president . why did n't democrats do something then ? this is why glen ford called democrats the more effective evil . the trump fox continues to push you into the mouth of democrat wolfs . look at how delicately the liberal press treats the obvious contradictions of the biden administration : `` it 's fair to ask whether the biden administration is beginning to prioritize economics over science , just as democrats once blasted trump for doing . '' https : //t.co/rbel9ptw7h the democrats have nothing to distinguish them from republicans then they are not trump & amp ; virginia showed that ai n't selling . if democrat party has any hope to survive they must overthrown their right-wing . https : //t.co/g2mnfitbqw why are u.s. authorities with some of their european lackeys committed to the dangerous & amp ; counterproductive strategy of expanding nato ? is this one of biden 's & amp ; democrats `` difference '' with trump policies - war in ukraine ? is this incompetence or madness ? https : //t.co/qzs5qsmh9x biden & amp ; neoliberal democrats have nothing but the highest contempt for the intelligence of their supporters . biden has not fulfilled any major campaign promises . democrats think the trump thing is going to be enough to hold control of congress . it wo n't . you see the kind of insidious influence trump has had on everyone ? even uncle joe is behaving like a white supremacist and we all know `` colored '' people 's lives matter for joe & amp ; neoliberal democrats . https : //t.co/xgxwzq0ozu this is what we wake up to on international human rights day , the u.s. involved in doing what it does the best - assaulting human rights . please do n't tell some us anything about the difference between trump & amp ; democrats because both are neofascists . https : //t.co/kzutvabzd8 the election in virginia demonstrated that running against trump was a non-started so the question is what will democrats run on in 2022 . the answer is - nothing . they have no message because they have no program that speaks to needs of working class that is catching hell . someone please tell me again the difference between right-wing neoliberal democrats & amp ; right-wing trump wing of capitalist class when in fact neoliberals are even more dangerous warmongers because they face no opposition from their rightist liberal base . https : //t.co/kq7oaj1hvm
