we tested if trump voters withdraw support if policies disadvantage them personally , looking at his tax cut . we asked them to predict their tax liability a couple weeks before the tax deadline , then asked again after they had filed their taxes return . our recent work shows that trump voters remain loyal even if they themselves are hurt by his ideas . i sincerely hope they do n't follow his dangerous health advice . https : //t.co/wtq8bsrcs2 importantly , trump voters who were made aware of their disappointing tax outcome downgraded the importance of ‘ lowering taxes ’ as a policy item . this might reflect cognitive dissonance , of supporting trump while also being negatively affected by his policies . bottom line : trump voters maintained support even if it hurt them personally . this raises important questions about the covid-19 crisis , and how far supporters will now go to disregard health-related information when it ’ s in conflict with their political allegiance .
